import React from 'react'
import styled from 'styled-components'
import { Flex, Cblock,Title, NewForm,ForInput,MyInput,Btn} from './register'
export default function Login() {
  return (
    (
        <Flex>
    <Cblock>
    <Title>Register</Title>
    <Clmn>
    <NewForm >
                <ForInput>
                <MyInput type='text'  placeholder='name' name='name'  />
    
                </ForInput>
                <ForInput>
                <MyInput type='email' placeholder='email' name='email'  />
    
                </ForInput>
                <ForInput>
                <MyInput type='number' placeholder='age' name='age'  />
    
                </ForInput>
                <ForInput>
                <MyInput type='password' placeholder='password' name='password'  />
                </ForInput>
                
    
    
                <Btn>Submit</Btn>
            
        </NewForm>
    </Clmn>
          
    </Cblock>
         
        </Flex>
      )
  )
}
